description:
In episode 1008, Jack and Miles are joined by host of the Live To Tape podcast Johnny Pemberton to discuss how Greg Abbot becoming an absurd parody of himself, Mitch McConnell’s power waning? Coachella does 180 on vaccines...but why? That Machine Gun Kelly / Megan Fox Interview and more!
